    All Times 9pm EST unless stated
    :zero: Monday
    :one: Tuesday
    :two: Wednesday
    :three: Thursday
    :four: Friday
    :five: Saturday noon EST
    :six: Saturday
    :seven: Sunday noon EST
    :eight: Sunday

    You may use this channel to post the draft tool and game URLs. Please remember to note who played what champions
